{"chapter_number":85,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":27,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"البروج","name_complex":"Al-Burūj","name_simple":"Al-Buruj","verses_count":22,"pages":[590,590],"meaning":{"text":"The Mansions of the Stars","en":"The Mansions of the Stars","id":"Gugusan Bintang"},"verses":[[[1,5910,"85:1","وَالسَّمَاءِ ذَاتِ الْبُرُوجِ",["I swear by the mansions of the stars,","Demi langit yang mempunyai gugusan bintang,"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[2,5911,"85:2","وَالْيَوْمِ الْمَوْعُودِ",["And the promised day,","dan demi hari yang dijanjikan."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[3,5912,"85:3","وَشَاهِدٍ وَمَشْهُودٍ",["And the bearer of witness and those against whom the witness is borne.","Demi yang menyaksikan dan yang disaksikan."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[4,5913,"85:4","قُتِلَ أَصْحَابُ الْأُخْدُودِ",["Cursed be the makers of the pit,","Binasalah orang-orang yang membuat parit (yaitu para pembesar Najran di Yaman),"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[5,5914,"85:5","النَّارِ ذَاتِ الْوَقُودِ",["Of the fire (kept burning) with fuel,","yang berapi (yang mempunyai) kayu bakar,"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[6,5915,"85:6","إِذْ هُمْ عَلَيْهَا قُعُودٌ",["When they sat by it,","ketika mereka duduk di sekitarnya,"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[7,5916,"85:7","وَهُمْ عَلَىٰ مَا يَفْعَلُونَ بِالْمُؤْمِنِينَ شُهُودٌ",["And they were witnesses of what they did with the believers.","sedang mereka menyaksikan apa yang mereka perbuat terhadap orang-orang mukmin."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[8,5917,"85:8","وَمَا نَقَمُوا مِنْهُمْ إِلَّا أَن يُؤْمِنُوا بِاللَّهِ الْعَزِيزِ الْحَمِيدِ",["And they did not take vengeance on them for aught except that they believed in Allah, the Mighty, the Praised,","Dan mereka menyiksa orang-orang mukmin itu hanya karena (orang-orang mukmin itu) beriman kepada Allah Yang Mahaperkasa, Maha Terpuji,"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[9,5918,"85:9","الَّذِي لَهُ مُلْكُ السَّمَاوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ ۚ وَاللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ شَهِيدٌ",["Whose is the kingdom of the heavens and the earth; and Allah is a Witness of all things.","yang memiliki kerajaan langit dan bumi. Dan Allah Maha Menyaksikan segala sesuatu."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[10,5919,"85:10","إِنَّ الَّذِينَ فَتَنُوا الْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ ثُمَّ لَمْ يَتُوبُوا فَلَهُمْ عَذَابُ جَهَنَّمَ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابُ الْحَرِيقِ",["Surely (as for) those who persecute the believing men and the believing women, then do not repent, they shall have the chastisement of hell, and they shall have the chastisement of burning.","Sungguh, orang-orang yang mendatangkan cobaan (bencana, membunuh, menyiksa) kepada orang-orang mukmin laki-laki dan perempuan lalu mereka tidak bertobat, maka mereka akan mendapat azab Jahanam dan mereka akan mendapat azab (neraka) yang membakar."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[11,5920,"85:11","إِنَّ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ لَهُمْ جَنَّاتٌ تَجْرِي مِن تَحْتِهَا الْأَنْهَارُ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ الْفَوْزُ الْكَبِيرُ",["Surely (as for) those who believe and do good, they shall have gardens beneath which rivers flow, that is the great achievement.","Sungguh, orang-orang yang beriman dan mengerjakan kebajikan, mereka akan mendapat surga yang mengalir di bawahnya sungai-sungai, itulah kemenangan yang agung."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[12,5921,"85:12","إِنَّ بَطْشَ رَبِّكَ لَشَدِيدٌ",["Surely the might of your Lord is great.","Sungguh, azab Tuhanmu sangat keras."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[13,5922,"85:13","إِنَّهُ هُوَ يُبْدِئُ وَيُعِيدُ",["Surely He it is Who originates and reproduces,","Sungguh, Dialah yang memulai pen-ciptaan (makhluk) dan yang menghidupkannya (kembali)."],590,30,59,236,null,null],[14,5923,"85:14","وَهُوَ الْغَفُورُ الْوَدُودُ",["And He is the Forgiving, the Loving,","Dan Dialah Yang Maha Pengampun, Maha Pengasih,"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[15,5924,"85:15","ذُو الْعَرْشِ الْمَجِيدُ",["Lord of the Arsh, the Glorious,","yang memiliki ‘Arsy, lagi Mahamulia,"],590,30,59,236,null,null],[16,5925,"85:16","فَعَّالٌ لِّمَا يُرِيدُ",["The 